{"tid":1459643,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一句同香港人打氣既說話！！","createTime":"2019-08-12T18:44:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T19:50:59.000Z","uid":296687,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d58b30aa5e6224bc83ccb839ddce4207330b1e5f","tid":1459643,"uid":296687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T18:44:31.000Z","msg":"其實812機場和你飛係成功！<br />\n大家唔好再互屌喇我地冇輸到仼何野！<br />\n冇送人頭，冇流血，冇受傷，冇被拉！<br />\n<br />\n到今時今日，我地一齊奮戰咗2個幾月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n望住身邊既人愈嚟愈冇希望 愈嚟愈頹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但直到前面有post話我地今次812贏到笑 <br />\n我地完全唔需要衝 學和理非咁只係涼冷氣都可以贏返次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都認同 見有同路人重拾返少少希望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係呢到好想同大家打氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我先<br />\n<br />\n記得之前睇過一條片係訪問外國人對呢件事既睇法<br />\n有一句 係引用「馬丁路德金 Martin Luther King 」既一句說話 想送比大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;We stop being ourselves, when we stop standing up for the things that matter.&rdquo;<br />\n「當我們不再為重要的事情挺身而出時，我們就不再是我們自己了。」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港人加油，萬事小心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"52bb5b2082e6954a1aae8b3c57b7c534e1c496a7","tid":1459643,"uid":296687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T18:47:22.000Z","msg":"香港人加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好放棄<br />\n唔想再見到身邊有人放棄"},{"pid":"fc0490eb87b3e991f6246601c76f542d67fa41cc","tid":1459643,"uid":296687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T18:49:06.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"f6b604101dc3f7d9c10ab00c2f22e0fbeb829dd5","tid":1459643,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T18:50:26.000Z","msg":"[緊急分析]法！不！責！眾！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1456781\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1456781</a>"},{"pid":"61d215bc40c9eab254264d6db574a5d9486a5680","tid":1459643,"uid":296687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T18:53:22.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"87616c548530ec53c0bea4a6cb6b82b6b5c05553","tid":1459643,"uid":296687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T18:53:35.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"6036b51bd2b4b53c7ed00627ab44bfed7dfd36c6","tid":1459643,"uid":296687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T18:53:48.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"afc27fdea8ec480c331abd195b796ecc25691172","tid":1459643,"uid":296687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T18:54:03.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"ab17bb40248b226b2d99f4b3e83672b49e3665d0","tid":1459643,"uid":296687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T18:54:15.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"99460147c291bba357b0821e8745a20b1608f1f1","tid":1459643,"uid":296687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T18:54:31.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"f0f8a08a70ba4b71f451d2276226e71c3cd9283b","tid":1459643,"uid":296687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T18:54:45.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"c1dc1c46cf14041c1284c12cfa96266f20e75436","tid":1459643,"uid":296687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T18:55:02.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"169b834ad82186c5095b6d136a01f8108f4e616b","tid":1459643,"uid":296687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T18:55:12.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"1b8197eddae2f4f72dce7877ac2e61479d0d7df6","tid":1459643,"uid":296687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T18:55:25.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"168233cf5de6224aff1a2fb7a79099d5e0cbd32c","tid":1459643,"uid":305822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-